title: Can you tell me a underrated song that deserves 1 billion views? - Quora

response.answer_text: Here’s the list not a song: Almost all songs of Super Junior.Yellow by coldplayHallelujah by PentatonixYou are the reason by Calum ScottNew face by PSYSomeone you loved by Lewis Capaldi, though it’s recent one but even 190 millions views is also low for this song.Winter bear and Sweet night by Kim Taehyung (V) of BTS. Please look after them.Without me by HalseyI don’t wanna live forever by zayn mailk and taylor swiftWavin’ flag by K’NAANOne love by BlueSongs of Backstreet BoysWhere is the love? by The Black Eyed PeasAirplanes by B.o.B. ft Hayley WilliamsThe real slim shady and Godzilla by Eminem.
